'''Smallmouth Bass''' is a {{Rarity|Common}} fish found in [[Terrapin Island]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Smallmouth Bass is a popular freshwater fish known for its fighting spirit and preference for clear, cool waters. It has a streamlined body with a greenish-brown coloration and distinctive horizontal stripes.  It can be found in plenty of freshwaters, but is native to Terrapin Islands filtered water.|Bestiary Entry}}

